headline: Familiar Destinations Top Agoda's Family Travel Ranking
summary: Digital travel platform Agoda has unveiled its family travel ranking, listing top family destinations for 2024. The ranking offers insights into how family travel preferences have evolved from the previous year. The list, which sees Tokyo take the crown, highlights both continuity and change in international travel trends for families.
